OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOvercast
OL,6,Fwith widespread low cloud soon
OL,7,Fdeveloping into the evening. Outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain will spread northwards across
OL,9,Fthe region during the night, some of
OL,10,Fwhich are likely to be heavy and
OL,11,Fpersistent. Winds will remain
OL,12,Fgenerally light and variable.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FRain and low cloud will
OL,15,Fgradually clear eastwards through the
OL,16,Fmorning, giving way to a few brighter
OL,17,Fspells in the afternoon with scattered
OL,18,Fshowers, some possibly heavy and
OL,19,Fthundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
