OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fstarts settled, but a few isolated
OL,7,Fshowers developing in the afternoon.
OL,8,FTuesday and Wednesday become more
OL,9,Funsettled with showers, some heavy at
OL,10,Ftimes, and temperatures turning cooler.
